{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":46536,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":7700,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"抽象代数？","timestamp":1593164243,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":46553,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":7700,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"说话没问题，你用抽象话表达意思还必须让别人懂就**","timestamp":1593164329,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":46562,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":7700,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Bob: 这个懂得都懂，不懂的我也没希望你懂，这也冒犯到一些人了吗","timestamp":1593164373,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":46604,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":7700,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"没有问题，只是多数喜欢说抽象话的人的价值观和另一群人的价值观冲突，于是火烧到了语言身上。或者说抽象/狗粉丝本身成为了一种身份认同，认同他们的价值观的人才会加入，同时加入的人无意识强化这种价值观；另一部分人也是一样的。就是群体极化效应。个人看来，现在是逢抽必反的那群人比较脑瘫。","timestamp":1593164601,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":46614,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":7700,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Carol: 懂哥","timestamp":1593164689,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":46825,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":7700,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"确实最初让人反感的不是抽象话而是狗粉丝","timestamp":1593166715,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":47367,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":7700,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"这种事情见得多了，我只想说懂得都懂，不懂的我也不多解释，毕竟自己知道就好，细细品吧。你们也别来问我怎么了，利益牵扯太大，说了对你我都没好处，当不知道就行了，其余的我只能说这里面水很深，牵扯到很多东西。详细情况你们自己是很难找的，网上大部分已经删除干净了，所以我只能说懂得都懂。","timestamp":1593173147,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":2,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":7700,"reply":7,"tag":null,"text":"说抽象话本身有什么问题？","timestamp":1593164230,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782585,"url":"","vote":{}}}